<div class="third">

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
        <h3>Félicitations! Ton dossier est prêt !</h3>
        <h5>Tu peux maintenant télécharger l'entête en pdf et y joindre tes justificatifs pour l'envoyer aux propriétaires des appartements qui t'intéressent, ou uploader tes justificatifs pour avoir un dossier consultable en ligne directement ! ouh ouh</h5>
        <%= link_to "Uploader mes justificatifs !", "#", class: "btn custom-btn", disabled: "disabled" %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="land">
          <%= image_tag "growing.png", style:" <width:400px;", class: "landing_img" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="document" class="container">
    <div>
      <%= image_tag "logo_doc.png", class: "dossier_logo" %>
    </div>
    <div class="dossier_candidates">
      <% x = @candidates.size %>
      <% @candidates.each do |candidate| %>
        <% now = Time.now.utc.to_date %>
        <% bd = now.year - candidate.birthdate.year - (candidate.birthdate.to_date.change(:year => now.year) > now ? 1 : 0) %>
        <h4><i class="fa fa-user"></i> <%= "#{candidate.firstname} #{candidate.lastname}" %> - <%= bd %> ans</h4>
        <p><i class="fa fa-envelope-o"></i> hello@world.com</p>
        <p><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> (01) 42 42 42 42</p>

        <% @bio_name = "#{candidate.firstname} #{candidate.lastname}" %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <ul class="list-inline">
      <li><%= image_tag "http://placehold.it/150x150", class: "img-circle biopic"%></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="separator">
      <h4>Biography</h4>
    </div>
    <div><p class="dossier_bio"> My name is <%= @bio_name %> and I have been married for ___ years. I'm expecting a child so we decided to look for a bigger place. I've been working as a ___________ at ____________ for __ years and my husband is a ___________ at ____. We don't have pets and we are non-smokers. Here's our dossier for your appraisal, I really do hope it pleases you, Thank you! <%= @bio_name %></p></div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="revenue"> <%= "Total Revenue :"%> <%= @revenue_total = @candidates.first.income + @candidates.last.income  %></h4>
      <h6>environ <%= @revenue_total * 12%>€ par an</h6>
    </div>
    <div class="separator">
      <h4>Employement and Income</h4>
    </div>
     <div>
      <h4></h4>
      <h6><%= @candidates.first.status%></h6>
      <h6>depuis: </h6>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h4 class="revenue">Past Rentals</h4>
    </div>
    <div class="separator">
      <h4>References</h4>
    </div>
  </div>

<!-- commented modal -->
  <!-- Sign-up Modal -->
  <div data-backdrop="static" class="modal show" id="signUp" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
      <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
          <!-- <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"> -->
          <!--  <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span> -->
          <!-- </button> -->
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8">
              <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Génial !</h4>
              <p>Votre dossier est maintenant prêt. Pour exploiter 100% du service, vous devez confirmer la création de votre compte</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 hidden-xs hidden-sm col-md-4">
              <%= image_tag "account.png", class: "landing_img" %>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-body text-justify">
          <!-- Your signup form -->
          <%# render "devise/registrations/new" %>
          <%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => registration_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
          <div><%= f.label :email %><br />
            <%= f.email_field :email, class: "form-control input-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div><%= f.label :password %><br />
            <%= f.password_field :password, class: "form-control input-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div><%= f.label :password_confirmation %><br />
            <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, class: "form-control input-lg" %>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <%= f.submit "Sign up", class: "btn btn-warning" %>
          </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
<!-- test -->
</div>
